Description
-----------

The mask\_backleft keywork only allows sound from the shader to be
outbut through the rear left surround sound speaker in a 5.1 setup.

Usage
-----

    mask_backleft

Example
-------

    ship_engine_rumble
    {
        mindistance 100
        maxdistance 1000
        volume 10
        looping
        mask_backleft
        shakes .1
        sound/last_stand/loop_rumble_backleft_b.wav
    }

Notes
-----

When this is in use, sound only comes from that channel when 5.1
surround is used. If you use 2 channel (stereo) sound the channel will
be muted and this sound will not be played.

